Know Your Customer (KYC) requirements , back up services, usage calculator, Frequently Asked Questions 
(FAQs) and Safaricom Cloud access.  
3.2 We may provide you with other Safaricom Products and Services which  may include :  
▪ information on Safaricom promotions, products and tariffs ;  
▪ Social Network Support which includes a link to all Safaricom Call Centre social media platforms and 
other availab le alternative channels.  
▪ Payment Services which includes M -Pesa Merchant services, M -PESA Agency services, KYC 
verifications, agent locations, pay bill numbers, set limits and notifications, reversal requests and a 
link to Safaricom online shop.
